cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper deals with the translation of 3D point-clouds to 2D images, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) techniques. The use of conditional Generative Adversarial Networks (cGAN) also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the evaluation of the method on datasets involves multimedia (cs.MM) aspects.
